.TH "ep93xx_dma_tx_status" 9 "ep93xx_dma_tx_status" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ep93xx_dma_tx_status \- check if a transaction is completed
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "enum dma_status" ep93xx_dma_tx_status
.BI "(struct dma_chan *chan "  ","
.BI "dma_cookie_t cookie "  ","
.BI "struct dma_tx_state *state "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "chan" 12
channel
.IP "cookie" 12
transaction specific cookie
.IP "state" 12
state of the transaction is stored here if given
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function can be used to query state of a given transaction.
